{"tid":1888684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨鐵 : 本年度按可加可減機制提供優惠 抵銷加幅","createTime":"2020-02-20T10:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T11:00:46.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1eecf1941e3650469ba340a482ec568ea00d086d","tid":1888684,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"港鐵宣布凍結今年票價，行政總裁金澤培表示，如果可加可減機制顯示港鐵需要減價，港鐵會跟從，否則港鐵會提供相應優惠，抵銷加幅。<br />\n<br />\n金澤培又表示，港鐵最近乘客量及車站商業收入亦受很大影響，加上港鐵成本不輕，但希望與港人共度時艱。至於中小租戶2月及3月份免租一半，金澤培表示，港鐵於4月會再審視情況。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷表示，港鐵沙中綫延誤及超支，又曾經發生出軌意外，表現並不值得加價，今次因應疫情凍結票價，亦算是聆聽民意，希望港鐵及其他大企業如果有能力，可以提出更多惠及市民的措施，協助市民渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509773-20200220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509773-20200220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=49dba312\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509773-20200220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3ea4bdd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509773-20200220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8f7c3e2dc8abeed1c5f88298b6c22fa4109bfd0d","tid":1888684,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"減價都唔撘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}